OBJECT:
	corpse 


SYNOPSIS:
	inherit "std/corpse";


DESCRIPTION:
	This is jsut a special container which autodestructs after a
	specific time. It is used when monsters or players die.

	There is one function

	SetName(string name)
	  gives the corpse a name and starts the decaying process.



INHERITANCE TREE:
	corpse
	  `-container


SEE ALSO:
	properties(C), units(C)
